      'FIX C вҖ” ACCELERATION EVENT LOGIC: Entry threshold stays at 1.5 m/sВІ. Hysteresis continuation added at 1.2 m/sВІ to prevent fragmentation. Acceptance now requires sampleCount >= 2 AND deltaKmh >= 4.0 (removed sub-second duration filter, replaced with 1s-compatible sample-count logic). Rich metadata added: deltaKmh, sampleCount, mergedCount, startSpeedBand.',
